Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:14.79,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}You changed me so much I don't remember what I was like before we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:19.26,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The breeze caresses our cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:21.26,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Lullaby of Birdland...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:25.60,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}As we run down the slope,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:29.52,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}our flimsy shadows extend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:34.44,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's like a neverending summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:40.24,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It feels like when we snuck into the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:46.16,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Yeah, let's swim with our clothes on. Jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.49,0:01:48.83,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's an intense spiral of temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:53.33,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}A beat pierces my heart. A strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:57.05,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It vanishes after a quick spark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:59.84,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Even on bad days, I dress up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:04.72,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}and dance to some swing. The music quickly surrounds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:07.56,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}What is this dance exactly? I can't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:16.82,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Don't leave me. It's stuck in my head, and I can't get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:19.90,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The melody...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:25.70,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}is like love.
