Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:15.92,apollon main,Boy 1,0,0,0,,This is the birth of the \Nlegendary duo of East High!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:17.79,apollon main,Photography Club,0,0,0,,Could you stand closer to each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:20.12,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.12,0:00:21.04,apollon main,Photography Club,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:23.69,apollon main,Girl,0,0,0,,Hey, when did you two become friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:25.81,apollon main,Girl,0,0,0,,Where do you practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.81,0:00:28.06,apollon main,Girl,0,0,0,,{\a6}How do you play in such perfect unison?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.84,0:00:30.47,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen, let's get out of here. \NWhen I count to five, run left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.06,0:00:30.47,apollon main,Girl,0,0,0,,{\a6}You don't have to hide anything from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:32.47,apollon main,Girl,0,0,0,,{\a6}Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:31.81,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.81,0:00:32.47,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.83,0:00:33.94,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:34.83,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:35.47,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:37.43,apollon main,Photography Club,0,0,0,,They're running off again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:38.18,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ri!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.49,0:00:43.48,apollon main,Girl 2,0,0,0,,Aw, come on! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:48.08,apollon main,Yamaoka,0,0,0,,Shit. The girls were supposed \Nto be chasing after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:51.24,apollon main,Yamaoka,0,0,0,,Right now, those guys are just like The Beatles!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:53.47,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,I've learned from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:56.24,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,Forget about next year's festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:59.15,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,I'm looking even further ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:02.73,apollon main,Seiji,0,0,0,,I'll go so far that they'll \Nnever be able to catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:38.88,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Pops! Sorry I haven't been coming recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:43.12,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Huh? He's not here. Maybe in the basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:44.72,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:51.23,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie, would you check to see if Jun's down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:53.05,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:56.04,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's not summer vacation, \Nso why would he be—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:59.85,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Oh, a lot's happened while \Nyou boys weren't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:03.12,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,But he's not here now. He left last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:07.70,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Anyway, I haven't seen you in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:08.62,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:11.37,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Richie-rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:15.66,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,My piano trio is finally together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:23.14,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Junichi was disowned by his father \Nright after he came back this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:24.88,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Disowned?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:27.94,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Well, first he went against his parents' \Nwishes by going to college in Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:31.01,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,but then he stopped going to school
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.01,0:03:34.02,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,and got wrapped up in political activism.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:37.59,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,When the prodigal son wandered back home,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:40.28,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,it's no wonder his dad was furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:43.62,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,He wasn't allowed to set foot in his family's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:48.79,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,and soon after, I ran into him at the bar, three sheets to the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.96,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,so I let him take refuge here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:52.71,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:57.03,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Did he leave because of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:04:01.47,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,No, no. He happened to \Nfind a cheap room to rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:03.50,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.18,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:11.53,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:14.80,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Do not mope your life away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:19.48,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Playing one good session will drive \Naway those blues, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:25.20,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Never mind! Forget I did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:30.50,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I get it, Mr. Bill Evans, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:34.75,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,All right! What do you say we play a session \Nso I can work off this gloominess?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.59,apollon main,Yukari,0,0,0,,Junichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:49.97,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:55.39,apollon main,Yukari,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:57.98,apollon main,Yukari,0,0,0,,Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.91,apollon main,Yukari,0,0,0,,What made him change this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:14.95,apollon main,Yukari,0,0,0,,That one winter day, in the \Nbasement... What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:20.10,apollon main,Yukari,0,0,0,,Did he just do it on a whim?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:40.24,apollon main,Yukari,0,0,0,,Even if I knock, he may not open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:50.02,apollon main,Yukari,0,0,0,,Or would he look at me again \Nwith those vacant eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:59.54,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Sorry, but that doesn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:09.47,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,You win. That angry face of \Nyours is my Achilles heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:13.43,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,You had that same expression \Nwhen we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.64,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,I remember it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:23.36,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do? Just go home? Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.92,apollon main,Girl A,0,0,0,,Mukae!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:44.92,apollon main,Girl A,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Would you give this to Nishimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:49.43,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um, wouldn't it be better if \Nyou gave it to him yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:53.76,apollon main,Girl A,0,0,0,,Oh, I couldn't! I'd be \Ntoo nervous! So, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:55.93,apollon main,Girl,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:06:59.94,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:04.69,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,It's been a while since the festival, but \Nyour popularity hasn't waned, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:06.65,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:24.00,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,What am I staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:27.84,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Am I jealous? It has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.13,apollon main,Tokie,0,0,0,,Ri!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:32.68,apollon main,Tokie,0,0,0,,Hey, which scarf design \Ndo you think is better?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:37.72,apollon main,Tokie,0,0,0,,Actually, there's this guy I kind of like,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:40.23,apollon main,Tokie,0,0,0,,and I'm thinking about making one for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.27,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.15,apollon main,Tokie,0,0,0,,I can't say yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.36,apollon main,Tokie,0,0,0,,But how about you, Ri?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:47.98,apollon main,,0,0,0,,Isn't there someone you wanna knit for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:50.49,apollon main,Tokie,0,0,0,,Come on, let's knit together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:54.95,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,But I don't have anyone to give it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:58.41,apollon main,Tokie,0,0,0,,Oh, be honest with yourself, Ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:01.62,apollon main,Tokie,0,0,0,,Just now, you were staring \Nat a certain someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:05.08,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,It's not what you think. \NDon't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:09.88,apollon main,Tokie,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Nishimi \Nis just a friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.34,apollon main,Tokie,0,0,0,,Sorry! I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:18.72,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,What a beautiful color.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.73,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I bet Kaoru would look good in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:27.65,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:31.11,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,What's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.40,apollon main,,0,0,0,,Why is my heart beating so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:38.41,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,That day in the basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:41.58,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I almost forgot about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:45.04,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,You wanna know why I did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:49.17,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Was it a little too stimulating for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:53.09,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Sorry. I was just feeling kind \Nof mischievous at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:58.43,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:00.93,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:03.18,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Didn't you come in here because \Nyou wanted me to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:07.44,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,What were you hoping for? \NA declaration of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:10.19,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Sorry to disappoint you, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.44,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,But this is the kind of guy I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:20.41,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,You've stopped fighting back.\NAre you resigned to it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:21.62,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.87,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,"If I act like this, \Nshe'll probably run off."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.08,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Is that what you're thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:32.84,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:35.34,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,You can do what you want with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.01,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:44.77,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Go home. Don't ever come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:48.23,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,I'm not the same person I was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:52.11,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,I dropped out of college, and my family disowned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:57.07,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Society gave me the boot, and \Nthere's no way for me to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:10:01.08,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Get close to me and your life will be ruined too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:04.66,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,If you understand what I'm sayin', \Nget the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:17.72,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:21.47,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,I'm sick of you calling me "young lady,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:24.47,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,so I thought I'd get rid of that image you have of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:28.48,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,If you're not the same person you once were,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:33.15,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,then I can become a new person too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:41.66,apollon main,Muroi,0,0,0,,Katsuragi, I'm gonna become a new me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:43.03,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:51.29,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Don't go throwing away something \Nprecious for someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:04.14,apollon main,Arita,0,0,0,,So you're the Katsuragi \NI've heard so much about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:08.18,apollon main,Arita,0,0,0,,How about saying something \Nto mark the occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.02,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.27,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,I'm just passing through,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:17.40,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,but I'd like to share my opinion on \Nwhat a college {\i1}should{\i0} be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:22.03,apollon main,Muroi,0,0,0,,Katsuragi... You inspired me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.12,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Muroi, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:27.33,apollon main,Muroi,0,0,0,,Listening to your speech made \Nme feel ashamed of myself
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.42,apollon main,Muroi,0,0,0,,for doing nothing but studying for exams and playing music.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.50,apollon main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\blur1.15\fax0.1\fs29\fnBarbedorT\frz349.25\org(478,593)\pos(343.2,596.4)\frx350\fry334}The Decline of a False System
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:41.51,apollon main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H2B2D32&\blur1.15\bord0\shad0\fs30\frx16\fry2\frz11.732\pos(750,331)}Strike Against\N Rising Tuition
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:41.51,apollon main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur1.15\bord0\shad0\fs30\c&H050A0A&\frx0\fry10\frz347.463\pos(183,631)}All Students on Strike
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:41.51,apollon main,Muroi,0,0,0,,Hey, Katsuragi, in the next battle, \Nif something were to happen to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.89,apollon main,Muroi,0,0,0,,would you take over for me, even just for a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.85,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Arita, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:59.40,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Hey, Muroi. Come over once \Nin a while to play the sax.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:05.28,apollon main,Muroi,0,0,0,,Katsuragi! Arita's been arrested!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:17.75,apollon main,Muroi,0,0,0,,The bones are shattered,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.97,apollon main,Muroi,0,0,0,,so the doc told me my fingers won't \Nbe able to move like they used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:23.34,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Wh-What about the sax?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:24.76,apollon main,Muroi,0,0,0,,I can't play anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:28.68,apollon main,Muroi,0,0,0,,Don't look so glum, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:32.39,apollon main,Muroi,0,0,0,,Now I can dump everything I don't \Nneed and just focus on the movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:36.23,apollon main,Muroi,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become a new me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:44.91,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:47.41,apollon main,Guy,0,0,0,,Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:48.95,apollon main,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:49.91,apollon main,Guy,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:03.72,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,I don't wanna see any more people \Nget hurt because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:11.81,apollon main,Yukari,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened to you, \Nand I don't intend to ask about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:17.19,apollon main,Yukari,0,0,0,,But I can see that you're hurt deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:22.28,apollon main,Yukari,0,0,0,,Can't I support you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:26.53,apollon main,Yukari,0,0,0,,Am I being too pushy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:32.66,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.67,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,You're a pushy woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:55.52,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Maybe I should stop takin' naps on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:58.57,apollon main,Girl 1,0,0,0,,Hey, wasn't that Yurika?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:00.94,apollon main,Girl 1,0,0,0,,Was she called in by the teacher again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:04.03,apollon main,Girl 2,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yurika's been acting weird these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:06.28,apollon main,Girl 2,0,0,0,,She's totally changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:09.12,apollon main,Girl 2,0,0,0,,What happened to that innocence she used to have?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:11.08,apollon main,Girl 1,0,0,0,,Maybe something happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:14.12,apollon main,Girl 2,0,0,0,,I asked her that, but she wouldn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:18.21,apollon main,Girl 1,0,0,0,,Well, since she cut her hair \Nlike that, could it mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:19.55,apollon main,Girl 1,0,0,0,,she's got a broken heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:23.59,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What the hell happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:25.34,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What'd he do to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.85,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,So you're Sentaro, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.60,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Do you like jazz?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:37.36,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Jun has been like a brother to me ever since I first met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:40.36,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I wanted to get good at jazz like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:41.94,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Be strong like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.86,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Become cool like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:47.37,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I tried to follow in his footsteps \Nevery step of the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:50.70,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,thinking I'd catch up someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.00,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Hey, Sen-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:55.83,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Your woman forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:04.97,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,If he would just talk to me, maybe I'd understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:11.81,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,But if he did something to {\i1}her{\i0}, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:20.44,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,J-Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:22.69,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I need to talk to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:29.16,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:30.66,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:38.33,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Shit. He's the one person I didn't \Nwant to find out about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.29,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,But what else could you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:44.05,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,He was bound to find out sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:50.30,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:53.81,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I knew she was beyond my \Nreach from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:57.73,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I knew it. Or I thought I did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:12.99,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I don't understand myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:16.71,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,When I'm with Kaoru,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:20.21,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I can really feel at ease \Nand have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:25.34,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,No. I decided long ago on \Nthe person that I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:28.97,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hi, Ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:31.97,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Is Sen here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:35.22,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:40.81,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Knitting? Why would she bother hiding that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:02.00,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey! Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:07.21,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:11.80,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:16.39,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You're obviously acting strangely \Ntoday. Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.23,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I saw 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:20.19,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:24.06,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,When I went to Jun's apartment, she was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:28.65,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Y-You're sure you saw her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:29.19,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:33.41,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,And of all people, it had to be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:35.12,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,That's what hurts the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:38.79,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:40.25,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,There's nothin' I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:44.75,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You've still got it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:49.80,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Even though you were jilted, you've \Nstill got someone who cares for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.51,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's like they say, you can't \Nsee the forest for the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:57.56,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,And those trees are so tall, you must \Nnot be able to see a damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:01.39,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Why don't you try looking more carefully?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:03.90,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Isn't it high time you realized it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:05.56,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Wh-What're you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:08.57,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Figure it out for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.49,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:16.66,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:20.00,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You just got here and you're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:22.62,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Yeah. I've got something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:24.71,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Are you done knitting for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:29.50,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sorry. I couldn't help glancing at it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.47,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:38.31,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ri, you're blushing! \NWas I right on the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.93,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Well, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:43.31,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Wait a min—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:50.48,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm sure this is for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:54.86,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't have a relapse! \NThis doesn't hurt at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:02.16,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,I won't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.87,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,You and this man from God knows where...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.75,0:19:09.09,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Yurika, you're being tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:12.17,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,What do you know, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:17.47,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth! I'll bring home a \Nsuitable partner for you before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:22.56,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,So don't meet with this man again, \NYurika. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:29.06,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,Yurika, your father is just \Ntalking to you like that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:30.77,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,because he's worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:37.03,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,You're a girl, so you have to \Ntake better care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:41.87,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,Just in case, keep next Saturday open, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:44.66,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,I made an appointment for \Nyou at the gynecologist.
