Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:17.49,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie, that rat. Throws out hints, then goes home...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:22.28,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Someone who cares for me? Like my family?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:23.95,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Is that what he meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:28.96,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,So you're gonna be the Virgin Mary
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:31.54,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,in the Christmas Nativity play, huh, Sa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:34.59,apollon main,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Yeah. But I'm nervous about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:37.01,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Hashiguchi will be there to see you too,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:38.26,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,so you have to do your best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:40.93,apollon main,Sachiko,0,0,0,,D-Don't mention him! I don't care if he...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:44.60,apollon main,Kota,0,0,0,,Sis, you're the one that said you're \Ngonna marry him when you grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:48.27,apollon main,Sachiko,0,0,0,,What?! That was a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:53.27,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um, Sentaro, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:57.24,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,When I grow up, I wanna get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:02.74,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Isn't it high time you realized it?
